{"tid":1861292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭真係完美咁演繹到一個無料扮四條既廢柴","createTime":"2020-02-04T05:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T12:38:29.000Z","uid":37528,"like":64,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4aa38690bca289c493ed5729e3edd1e2e89e0e12","tid":1861292,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"細過：<br />\n成日話以前係學校年年考第一，點知出到去CE得3個A，之後又話自己失手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做官：<br />\n然後之後做官，成日做到自己好打得呢個形象。實質就係厚顏無恥，講過唔算數，俾人屌打都扮無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做特首：<br />\n又係盡現自己厚顏無恥既一面。由送中開始，條柒婆根本一直輸緊。無論做咩決定都慢一拍，一開頭又做錯曬決定。到而家封關，既得罪大部分香港人，亦得罪埋支那人。<br />\n而家根本俾澳門玩緊，所有野同柒婆調轉做根本sure win<br />\n<br />\n呢條咁既廢柴，玩獨裁又唔撚識，要奶共又奶撚到兩邊不是人。要揀全港最廢既人，柒婆一定榜上有名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話咩年年考第一，笑撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係讀屎片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da56804590a2f09cc465b47b065dcc1c26077f5","tid":1861292,"uid":2267,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GhVKkvL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGhVKkvL.jpg&h=d79913e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aacde568cd0edfa18051906d439a61c67c9d155c","tid":1861292,"uid":224533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"所以林鄭同維尼咁夾"},{"pid":"c04dbb703e896aa735af91e92d4ae4d512e005c7","tid":1861292,"uid":5737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"歷史一定有佢個名<br />\n仲唔係年年第1？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0ac6ba424e467dd11c6c0a6ccd324ae5d0ddc7","tid":1861292,"uid":82640,"like"